Approach for model training :

🥇 Option 1 (Recommended): Create your own dataset.csv

Since your application already detects hands, this is the best approach.

Why?

✅ Matches your webcam setup
✅ Works with Indian users and different lighting conditions
✅ Small dataset size
✅ Much easier than image datasets
✅ Better accuracy for your project

Instead of storing images, store the 21 MediaPipe landmarks.

Each row:

gesture,x0,y0,z0,x1,y1,z1,...,x20,y20,z20

Example:

HELLO,0.52,0.63,-0.04,0.55,0.61,-0.03,...
THANKYOU,0.49,0.68,-0.02,...
YES,...
NO,...
Suggested target

Start with 20 gestures.

HELLO
THANKYOU
YES
NO
PLEASE
